ual
\end_layout

\end_inset

page is very informational and can be viewed with the command:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Quote

\family typewriter
man pacman
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
To exit, press
\family typewriter
\series bold
 q
\family default
\series default
.
\end_layout

