\begin_layout Plain Layout

\family typewriter
sudo pacman-mirrors -f 0
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Quote

\family typewriter
sudo pacman-mirrors
\begin_inset Index idx
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Pacman-mirrors
\end_layout

\end_inset

 -f 0
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
This will test the speed of all currently available mirrors and set your
 machine to use the best for you.
 Once this command has completed, you should force a download of the package
 lists with the command:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Quote

\family typewriter
sudo pacman -Syyu
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Выбор зеркал
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
If you would like more control over which mirrors to use, run the command:
\begin_inset Float figure
wide false
sideways false
status open

